name: Unidentified_Frizznoth_Nihil
content: A Frizznoth was a Nihil marauder, holding the rank of Strike in the Tempest of Tempest Runner Lourna Dee, serving aboard the starship Lourna Dee. During the Battle of Galov, they escaped after the Nihil, outgunned and outnumbered by the Galactic Republic and Jedi Order forces, were forced to evacuate the starship. After the Frizznoth escaped, they went to Cerea, where they met with fellow Strike Andrik Keller. They gave Keller a tracking device which would reveal Dee's location. The Frizznoth later abandoned Keller after the two got into trouble on Fimster.
